    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Suy ra $d(DM, SB) = d(DM, (SBC)) = d(M, (SBC)) = \\frac{1}{2}d(A, (SBC))$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      802,
      1177,
      883
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Xét tam giác $\\Delta ACB$, có $AM = MB = MC = \\frac{1}{2}AB$ nên suy ra $\\Delta ACB$ vuông tại $C$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      905,
      163,
      940
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Do đó"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      82,
      963,
      452,
      1059
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\left. \\begin{array}{l} SA \\perp BC \\\\ AC \\perp BC \\end{array} \\right\\} \\Rightarrow BC \\perp (SAC)\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      1083,
      1032,
      1134
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Lại có $BC \\subset (SBC)$ nên suy ra $(SBC) \\perp (SAC)$ theo giao tuyến $SC$."
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      1158,
      858,
      1356
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned} \\text{Kẻ } AH \\perp SC &\\Rightarrow AH = d(A, (SBC)) = \\frac{SA \\cdot AC}{\\sqrt{SA^2 + AC^2}} = \\frac{3a}{2}. \\\\ &\\Rightarrow d(DM, SB) = \\frac{1}{2} \\cdot \\frac{3a}{2} = \\frac{3a}{4}. \\end{aligned}\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      1378,
      295,
      1418
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\text{Vậy } x = 3, y = 4\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      76,
      1442,
      273,
      1482
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\Rightarrow x = 3, y = 4\n$$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
